{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 33,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 234.218,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, cannot write all the things which were taught among my people;",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.103,
      "end": 7.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither am I mighty in writing,",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.512,
      "end": 9.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like unto speaking;",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.271,
      "end": 12.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for when a man speaketh by the power of the Holy Ghost",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.841,
      "end": 17.16,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the power of the Holy Ghost carrieth it unto the hearts of the children of men.",
      "verse": "33:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 17.84,
      "end": 22.763,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, there are many that harden their hearts against the Holy Spirit,",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 22.943,
      "end": 25.033,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it hath no place in them;",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 25.213,
      "end": 28.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they cast many things away which are written",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 29.062,
      "end": 31.616,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and esteem them as things of naught.",
      "verse": "33:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 32.296,
      "end": 35.222,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But I, Nephi, have written what I have written,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 35.402,
      "end": 37.631,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I esteem it as of great worth,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.811,
      "end": 39.761,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and especially unto my people.",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 39.941,
      "end": 42.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I pray continually for them by day,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 43.0,
      "end": 46.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and mine eyes water my pillow by night, because of them;",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 46.709,
      "end": 49.263,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cry unto my God in faith,",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 49.443,
      "end": 51.579,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I know that he will hear my cry.",
      "verse": "33:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 52.259,
      "end": 55.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I know that the Lord God will consecrate my prayers",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 55.783,
      "end": 57.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the gain of my people.",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 57.821,
      "end": 60.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the words which I have written in weakness",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 60.602,
      "end": 62.878,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be made strong unto them;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 63.058,
      "end": 65.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it persuadeth them to do good;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 65.653,
      "end": 68.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it maketh known unto them of their fathers;",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 68.666,
      "end": 70.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it speaketh of Jesus,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 70.657,
      "end": 73.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and persuadeth them to believe in him,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 73.252,
      "end": 75.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to endure to the end,",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 75.29,
      "end": 77.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is life eternal.",
      "verse": "33:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 77.688,
      "end": 80.242,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it speaketh harshly against sin,",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 80.422,
      "end": 82.883,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the plainness of the truth;",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 83.063,
      "end": 87.428,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, no man will be angry at the words which I have written",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 87.608,
      "end": 90.441,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save he shall be of the spirit of the devil.",
      "verse": "33:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 91.121,
      "end": 92.839,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in plainness;",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 93.019,
      "end": 94.598,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in truth;",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 94.778,
      "end": 96.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I glory in my Jesus,",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 96.583,
      "end": 98.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath redeemed my soul from hell.",
      "verse": "33:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 99.631,
      "end": 101.721,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have charity for my people,",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 101.901,
      "end": 103.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great faith in Christ",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 103.846,
      "end": 107.701,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I shall meet many souls spotless at his judgment-seat.",
      "verse": "33:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 108.381,
      "end": 110.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have charity for the Jew\u2014",
      "verse": "33:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 110.326,
      "end": 113.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say Jew, because I mean them from whence I came.",
      "verse": "33:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 114.117,
      "end": 116.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I also have charity for the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 116.665,
      "end": 119.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, for none of these can I hope",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 119.353,
      "end": 122.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except they shall be reconciled unto Christ,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 122.227,
      "end": 124.224,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and enter into the narrow gate,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 124.404,
      "end": 127.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and walk in the strait path which leads to life,",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 128.067,
      "end": 129.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continue in the path",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 130.105,
      "end": 132.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until the end of the day of probation.",
      "verse": "33:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 132.921,
      "end": 135.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 135.423,
      "end": 136.77,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Jew,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 136.95,
      "end": 138.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all ye ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 138.988,
      "end": 141.821,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "hearken unto these words and believe in Christ;",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 142.001,
      "end": 144.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if ye believe not in these words believe in Christ.",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 145.014,
      "end": 147.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if ye shall believe in Christ",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 147.237,
      "end": 149.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye will believe in these words,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 149.321,
      "end": 151.364,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are the words of Christ,",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 151.544,
      "end": 153.587,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he hath given them unto me;",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 153.767,
      "end": 156.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they teach all men that they should do good.",
      "verse": "33:10",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 157.466,
      "end": 159.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if they are not the words of Christ,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 159.829,
      "end": 160.944,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "judge ye\u2014",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 161.124,
      "end": 163.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for Christ will show unto you,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 163.347,
      "end": 165.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with power and great glory,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 165.524,
      "end": 167.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are his words,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 167.329,
      "end": 168.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at the last day;",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 169.042,
      "end": 172.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you and I shall stand face to face before his bar;",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 172.612,
      "end": 175.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye shall know that I have been commanded of him",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 175.718,
      "end": 177.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to write these things,",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 177.431,
      "end": 179.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "notwithstanding my weakness.",
      "verse": "33:11",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 180.015,
      "end": 182.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I pray the Father in the name of Christ",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 182.471,
      "end": 183.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that many of us,",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 184.137,
      "end": 185.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if not all,",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 185.478,
      "end": 187.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "may be saved in his kingdom",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 187.562,
      "end": 189.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at that great and last day.",
      "verse": "33:12",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 190.1,
      "end": 192.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my beloved brethren,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 192.602,
      "end": 195.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all those who are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 195.476,
      "end": 197.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all ye ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 197.514,
      "end": 200.904,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I speak unto you as the voice of one crying from the dust:",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 201.084,
      "end": 203.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Farewell until that great day shall come.",
      "verse": "33:13",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 204.318,
      "end": 207.662,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And you that will not partake of the goodness of God,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 207.842,
      "end": 210.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and respect the words of the Jews,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 210.437,
      "end": 211.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my words,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 212.15,
      "end": 216.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which shall proceed forth out of the mouth of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 216.602,
      "end": 219.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I bid you an everlasting farewell,",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 219.661,
      "end": 222.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for these words shall condemn you at the last day.",
      "verse": "33:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 223.499,
      "end": 225.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For what I seal on earth,",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 225.537,
      "end": 228.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be brought against you at the judgment bar;",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 228.643,
      "end": 230.872,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus hath the Lord commanded me,",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 231.052,
      "end": 232.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I must obey.",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 232.718,
      "end": 233.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "33:15",
      "lineIndex": 89
    }
  ]
}